Mantra

//MainActivity
Take your journey
Finding you special please to help you relax and grow is something that should be done 5-10 minutes every day. Open your mind and start your journey!
Press to let your journey begin
FOR EVERYDAY USAGE


//FirstActivity
Meditate
Focus on breathing in an out. Breath in from the mouth and out of your nose. Try t relax and keep your mind clear. Do this for 3-5 minutes. 

//SecondActivity
Silence
Turn off every electronic device and surrond yourself with the silence and listen to your inner self.

//ThirdActivity
Go walking
Take you headphones and head out to the nature for a relaxing walk.

//FourthActivity
Yoga
Now I want you to do five yoga exercises. Take the time you need and do not forget to breath slowly.

//FifthActivity
Tea time
We all now that a cup of tea is both good for your body and mental state. Now I want you to go make a cup of tea with and enjoy a relaxing time with either a book or in front of the tv.

//SixthActivity
Taking notes
Focus on what makes you happy and write down three of those things. Place the note in your pocket and be sure to always bring it with you.

//SeventhActivity
Thank somebody
Who makes you happy? Who brings you the most joy? Why not say "thank you" to that person?

//EightActivity
Read a book
Pick up your favorite book and lose yourself in its fantasy world!
